SUMMARY:Bird-in-Hand Half Marathon & 5k
DESCRIPTION:Experience a Race Like No Other.\nOld-world practices. Lush countryside. Hard-working people. All these things and more make the Bird-in-Hand Half Marathon a special experience. But some things can’t be described – like the sense of community that follows well after you cross the finish line. \nFriday\, September 11\, 2026 \n\n11 am – 7 pm –Race Expo & Packet Pick-up for all events\n4 – 8 pm – Pre-Race Pizza & Pasta Party\n6:10 pm – Kids Fun Run\n6:30 pm – 5K\n7:30 – 9 pm – Bonfire/S’mores Party\n\nSaturday\, September 12\, 2026 \n\n7:30 am – BIH Half Marathon\n10 am – 12pm – Community Picnic
